          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Extending Temporary Emergency Scheduling of Fentanyl Analogues Act</strong></p> <p>This bill extends until September 30, 2021, the temporary scheduling order issued by the Drug Enforcement Administration to place fentanyl-related substances in schedule I of the Controlled Substances Act. The temporary order expires on May 6, 2021.</p>]]>
